#eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Department of Social Development has deployed 300 social workers to KwaZulu-Natal. The trauma response task teams will provide psychosocial support to victims of the floods. READ: KZN flood deaths revised to 435, 13 further deaths were unrelated - Cele A total 435 people have died and thousands more are destitute. Watch the video above for more details on this story.